title: unplugged power and then (likely) barometer at SH
description: When installing the new pressure transducers, I   1) unplugged a wire out of a 12 v power supply, to add new wires. I wasn't sure which one it was, but after looking at the status page it looks like it was the barometric pressure gauge  2) I also accidentally unplugged the power for the data logger, then plugged it back in.

external_refs.identifier: unplugged power and then (likely) barometer at SH; see incident report IR_251
